Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.26,0:00:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的命运究竟是否在由看不见的力量或法则来掌控？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像神之手吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  至少有一点很明确
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的自由不受任何意志的支配
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.65,0:00:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.89,0:00:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霸王之卵!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.30,0:00:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我非常了解这个情景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.07,0:00:50.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你差点就把Griffith给害死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.84,0:00:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你的错!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有听说Hawks的事情?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.31,0:02:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在上次战争中失去了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.41,0:02:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知很确定  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.68,0:02:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部队说他们在Chuder's 城堡里遇到了一个巨大的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.22,0:02:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个巨大的恶魔?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.92,0:02:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我宣布那不是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.99,0:02:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他们失败的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连小孩玩花招都不如!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而Griffith成功地将城堡保护了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他们也损失了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:03:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还听说Griffith会被升级为贵族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也听说过
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.65,0:03:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的胜利使他在国王前的威望直线上升
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烦人!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.12,0:03:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王为什么把这个头衔给一个雇佣兵?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.16,0:03:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.40,0:03:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰之团的首领
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在战场时有过不好的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说你在战场上遇到过恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.85,0:03:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是不是那个恶魔伤了你?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.38,0:03:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你在黑暗中看到了一只狗  还以为他是魔鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.92,0:03:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:03:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我现在腿上负伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:05.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用你的血来祭我的刀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.98,0:04:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们全在这
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能走路吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你的错!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.23,0:05:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人在责怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:06.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caska只是说因为那很混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  你们现在去干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想去拜访Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们已经有客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大臣和主教们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界有点残忍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些老臣们鄙视Griffith 而且说他是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新来的雇佣兵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人却讨好他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.70,0:05:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们只是在帮他忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但Griffith至今仍然制无不胜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:50.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是Midland's最强军队的指挥官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.55,0:05:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.95,0:05:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有在听我说  对不?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.86,0:06:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在听
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎样?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:10.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管呢!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉过你在这等直到Griffith见客完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:17.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点关系都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.54,0:06:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想去见见负伤的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.77,0:06:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.81,0:06:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能进去的!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等到会议结束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:32.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.09,0:06:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:42.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.26,0:06:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ricket,你会跟我来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.27,0:06:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.05,0:07:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.27,0:07:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么一直这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.04,0:07:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么Griffith对你如此器重?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那全部都弄糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一会儿回来!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.47,0:07:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有点理解Guts的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后Griffith还是无法接近
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.35,0:08:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就像个陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.11,0:08:39.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.68,0:08:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该在那被Griffith给宰了!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.12,0:08:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对你的手下一点都不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.75,0:08:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就像一条疯狗!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么一直这样?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是你的错!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.73,0:08:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是你的错!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.67,0:09:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她到底是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经在边缘上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.35,0:09:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来可以拿起你的剑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管你被整得比我还惨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对昨天的事情道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:28.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说所有人都来看望我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我受伤的时候占便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些大臣们有意识的每天都来访问我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话  他们很烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.91,0:09:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而我别无它择
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nosferatu  Zodd
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:10:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽然有那么庞大的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.33,0:10:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇见它就像在做恶梦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在另一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.97,0:10:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有证明说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.70,0:10:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庞大的东西是存在的  尽管是在人类认知之上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它可能是个上帝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.35,0:10:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它更像个恶魔  不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.65,0:10:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.52,0:10:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我是怎么脱险的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在战斗中晕过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为在我脖子上的那个东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.01,0:11:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你和那个人是真正的朋友的话  记好这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.56,0:11:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这个人的野心成长时
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就会死!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:15.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的死是不可逃避的!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Zodd见过我带的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这看起来像是在保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得去谢谢那位预言者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又欠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.69,0:11:36.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3年前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.83,0:11:42.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉我你不想失去一个优秀的战士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是一名为你而战的战士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你差点就为了我而失去了你的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.57,0:11:49.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我只是一个普通的战士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.80,0:11:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不应该发生在你这个想出人投地的人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.74,0:11:56.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为我们3年前就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:08.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想知道理由吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想要为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:23.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次我决定用我的生命来保护你?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.05,0:12:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我只是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.62,0:12:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦白鹰先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起来好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.70,0:12:57.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的陛下!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:12:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨Guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么能在陛下的面前这样!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事  把头抬起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是呼吸一下空气
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.32,0:13:16.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我的陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都很兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那些战争的商讨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.60,0:13:24.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Alas,我想我不该再一次镇定下来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:28.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我介绍你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的弟弟the  Earl  of  Yurius
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.04,0:13:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是白龙的司令  而且是将来王冠的继承者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.88,0:13:38.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Griffith,很荣欣见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.61,0:13:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Griffith大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.02,0:13:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你带领Hawks胜利而骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很荣欣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在战场上的表现使我忘了我的年龄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还让我想上战场!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:14:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我想起来我年轻时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我在杀场上的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.87,0:14:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下  你不该这样跟一个指挥官说话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.84,0:14:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实该讲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.44,0:14:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些老的议员对你的存在很不满意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.45,0:14:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你的影响而感到危机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们觉的你的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:21.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能会影响到midland的军队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  士气和状态不能够给我们胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很关心我的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们生活在一个动乱的时代
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  我非常需要像你这样的人才
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像那些司令们一直以旧的规则办事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发誓要把我的地盘发展强壮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.85,0:14:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你很期盼  陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.39,0:15:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位小姐是谁?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.10,0:15:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的女儿Charlotte
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:10.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她对战士们很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她几乎从不走出这城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.51,0:15:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Charlotte,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.01,0:15:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个很内向的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我太宠我这个唯一的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅她Griffith大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来Charlotte
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.42,0:15:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.49,0:16:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽然敢碰公主的身体!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.66,0:16:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  老头子!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.00,0:16:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请原谅我的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:18.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高贵的Yurius
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.91,0:16:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:28.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没什么  父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得走了  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.53,0:17:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的需要一个原因
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.86,0:17:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次当我为你而死时?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说"为你"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道这到底是不是我想要的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会用我的剑来为他战斗!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  所有人!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道这个要塞有多重要吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道  先生!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.67,0:18:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们应该知道你们的历史!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.24,0:18:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着  因为我们占领了Doldrey,我们可以第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功的将敌人分开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  这个要塞是为军队
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.15,0:18:44.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻打midland而做准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着这条路!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这条在Doldrey和Kingdom's  territory之间的路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具有很高的军事价值
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而  我们的军队占领了这条桥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:58.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争的趋势改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样迫使他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.33,0:19:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把Midland的心脏地带暴露在我们眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个机密战术
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.27,0:19:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在Coborlwitz家庭流传了300年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想得到胜利 就要占领道路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.62,0:19:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要胜利  我们的防守必须更强壮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的防御已经计划好了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果敌人攻打我们的话  他们就得过这条桥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:33.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以Garrison里的最好战士会守在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个狭窄的石桥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.64,0:19:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能2人同时攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.77,0:19:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有Chuder最好的箭手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.67,0:19:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会站在大门上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:47.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的箭手会将在敌人一个一个过桥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:49.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们全部干掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.05,0:19:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会将敌人打得落花流水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了我这个超级的设想  我们不应该有损失!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以放心了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果敌人不从桥这攻击我们  而绕路到我们的后面怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.67,0:20:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你也不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这方圆8英里以内没有一个桥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有  这河很急  就连最好的马都过不去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果敌人作木筏怎么办  还有..
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如你所见 我们身处石地荒野
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:27.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能有那么多树来让他们做木筏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.42,0:20:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算他们做了足够的木筏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.56,0:20:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们一次也不能送足够的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.93,0:20:39.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非他们能用藤条做出船来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:59.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么Griffith一康复我们就得出击?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在战场里依靠我们
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  他们不是说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.62,0:21:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管最厉害的骑士出击  也无法将城堡击破
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说他们受了很大的挫伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说2/3的骑士在桥上被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:17.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？你是说真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.79,0:21:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轮到我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会将他们杀的片甲不留
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.22,0:23:14.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个男人都会为自己的野心而付出性命
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.35,0:23:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别是当他们年轻的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.12,0:23:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们无法控制自己火焰燃烧般的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.20,0:23:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去得到辉煌  去失去梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.73,0:23:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些可以逃避命运的人们
